                          <div class="media-body">
                            <h4 class="media-heading">Our Project</h4>This website was produced for the Bristol Museum & Art Gallery as part of an assessed software engineering project for second year computer scientists attending the University of Bristol. Working in collaboration with staff at the museum, the team of 6 students aimed to create a successful search tool designed to show the user the specific locations of items that can be found in the Bristol Museum & Art Gallery.
                          </div>
